---
import StaticPageLayout from '../../layouts/StaticPageLayout.astro';
---

<StaticPageLayout
  title="Privacy policy"
  description="A plain-language description of the minimal data footprint used by this static publication."
  kicker="Less collection, less explaining"
>
  <p>
    <strong>Effective July 11, 2026.</strong> Privacy questions can be sent to x771364026@gmail.com.
  </p>
  <h2>This MVP</h2><p>
    The site is statically generated. It has no accounts, comments, database, contact form, or
    newsletter submission endpoint. Search runs in the browser against a static Pagefind index.
  </p>
  <h2>Hosting logs</h2><p>
    Cloudflare may process request information needed to deliver and protect the site under its own
    privacy and retention terms. evidique does not operate a separate visitor database.
  </p>
  <h2>Future services</h2><p>
    If analytics or email signup is added, name the provider, data collected, purpose, retention,
    legal basis, and opt-out controls before enabling it.
  </p>
</StaticPageLayout>
